{"abstract":[{"code":"CustomParameterEncoding","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" 允许您定义和使用自定义的参数编码逻辑。","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/cryonet.CryoNet\/documentation\/CryoNet\/CustomParameterEncoding\/init(encoding:)"],"anchor":"Initializers","title":"Initializers"},{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/cryonet.CryoNet\/documentation\/CryoNet\/CustomParameterEncoding\/encode(_:with:)"],"anchor":"Instance-Methods","title":"Instance Methods"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/cryonet.CryoNet\/9Alamofire17ParameterEncodingP","doc:\/\/cryonet.CryoNet\/s8SendableP"],"title":"Conforms To"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"CustomParameterEncoding"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"overview","level":2,"text":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"此结构体遵循 Alamofire 的 "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ParameterEncoding"},{"type":"text","text":" 协议，使得您可以将任何自定义的参数编码行为"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"集成到 Alamofire 的请求流程中。这对于处理非标准或特定于业务的请求体格式非常有用。"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B","level":3,"text":"使用示例","type":"heading"},{"code":["\/\/ 示例：一个简单的自定义编码，将参数编码为 URL 查询字符串，即使是 POST 请求","let customURLEncoding = CustomParameterEncoding { urlRequest, parameters in","    var mutableRequest = try urlRequest.asURLRequest()","    guard let parameters = parameters else { return mutableRequest }","","    var urlComponents = URLComponents(url: mutableRequest.url!, resolvingAgainstBaseURL: false)","    urlComponents?.queryItems = parameters.map { URLQueryItem(name: $0.key, value: \"\\($0.value)\") }","    mutableRequest.url = urlComponents?.url","    return mutableRequest","}","","\/\/ 在请求中使用自定义编码","AF.request(\"https:\/\/api.example.com\/data\", method: .post, parameters: [\"id\": 123], encoding: customURLEncoding)","    .responseJSON { response in","        debugPrint(response)","    }"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"name":"Note","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"encodingClosure"},{"type":"text","text":" 闭包必须是 "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@Sendable"},{"type":"text","text":" 的，以确保在并发环境中安全执行。"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"通常情况下，您会通过 "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/cryonet.CryoNet\/documentation\/CryoNet\/CryoParameterEncoder\/custom(_:)","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" 枚举成员来使用此自定义编码。"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}],"type":"aside"},{"name":"See Also","style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/cryonet.CryoNet\/documentation\/CryoNet\/CryoParameterEncoder"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/cryonet.CryoNet\/documentation\/CryoNet\/CryoParameterEncoder\/custom(_:)"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/cryonet.CryoNet\/documentation\/CryoNet\/CustomParameterEncoding","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"externalID":"s:7CryoNet23CustomParameterEncodingV","modules":[{"name":"CryoNet"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"struct","title":"CustomParameterEncoding","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"CustomParameterEncoding"}],"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"CustomParameterEncoding","kind":"identifier"}]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/cryonet\/customparameterencoding"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["d